<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA57">
<l>ayaṉiṉṟa valviṉaiyai yañciṉē ṉañci</l>
<l>yuyaniṉ ṟiruvaṭiyē cērvā – ṉayaniṉṟa</l>
<l>naṉmālai koṇṭu namōnāraṇā veṉṉuñ</l>
<l>coṉmālai kaṟṟēṉ ṟoḻutu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I was afraid of the harsh karma that stood nearby. Having been afraid,</l>
<l>in order to join your holy feet so that I escape [fear],</l>
<l>worshipping with a favoured good [flower] garland, I have learned</l> 
<l>the word garland saying ‘obeissance, oh Nāraṇaṉ’.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
